---
layout: base.njk
register: forge
title: "Ask Finn"
description: "Enter Dreamborn's AI strategy room. Ask Finn, pressure-test your operating model, or book a strategy call."
socialTitle: "Ask Finn at Dreamborn"
socialDescription: "Bring your AI strategy to Dreamborn. Ask Finn, pressure-test the operating model, or book a call."
image: "https://imagedelivery.net/C0nJXN4TRwsrV5P_U5q4RQ/dreamborn-social-connect/public"
imageAlt: "Dreamborn Ask Finn social card for AI strategy conversations."
type: "website"
section: "Connect"
---

<main class="connect-room">
  <section class="connect-hero" aria-labelledby="connectHeroTitle">
    <div class="connect-hero__copy">
      <p class="ops-kicker">Connect / AI strategy room</p>
      <h1 id="connectHeroTitle">What&rsquo;s your AI strategy? Bring it here.</h1>
      <p>
        Dreamborn is an AI-native company. Finn can show you how it works, pressure-test what you&rsquo;re building, and route you to the right next conversation.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="connect-live-strip" aria-label="Dreamborn operating status">
      <span>Finn online</span>
      <span>Bezel live</span>
      <span>24 agents</span>
      <span>5 active now</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="connect-capabilities" aria-label="What Finn can do">
    <p class="ops-panel-label">Finn can</p>
    <div class="connect-capability-list">
      <button type="button" data-finn-prompt="Explain Bezel and how it runs an AI-native company.">Explain Bezel</button>
      <button type="button" data-finn-prompt="Pressure-test my AI strategy.">Pressure-test your AI strategy</button>
      <button type="button" data-finn-prompt="Map agent coverage for my company.">Map agent coverage for your company</button>
      <button type="button" data-finn-prompt="Show me live operating proof for Dreamborn.">Show live operating proof</button>
      <button type="button" data-finn-prompt="I want to book a strategy call.">Route you to a call</button>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="connect-stage" aria-label="Ask Finn">
    <div class="connect-chat-shell">
      <div class="connect-chat-topline">
        <div>
          <p class="ops-panel-label">Front-door operator</p>
          <h2>Start with Finn.</h2>
        </div>
        <span>live</span>
      </div>

      <div class="finn-chat" role="region" aria-label="Chat with Finn, Dreamborn's AI agent">
        <div class="finn-chat__header">
          <div class="finn-chat__avatar" aria-hidden="true">F</div>
          <div>
            <p class="finn-chat__name">Finn</p>
            <p class="finn-chat__subtitle">Dreamborn AI Agent</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="finn-chat__messages" id="finnMessages" role="log" aria-live="polite" aria-label="Conversation">
          <div class="message-bubble message-bubble--finn" role="article" aria-label="Finn: greeting">
            I&rsquo;m Finn. I can show you how Dreamborn runs, pressure-test your AI strategy, or help you decide whether this operating model fits your company.<br><br>
            What are you trying to build?
          </div>

          <div class="finn-typing" id="finnTyping" aria-hidden="true" aria-label="Finn is typing">
            <span class="finn-typing-dot"></span>
            <span class="finn-typing-dot"></span>
            <span class="finn-typing-dot"></span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="suggested-prompts" id="finnPrompts" role="group" aria-label="Suggested messages">
          <button class="prompt-pill" data-finn-prompt="Pressure-test my AI strategy">Pressure-test my AI strategy</button>
          <button class="prompt-pill" data-finn-prompt="Show me how Dreamborn runs">Show me how Dreamborn runs</button>
          <button class="prompt-pill" data-finn-prompt="What would Bezel do for my company?">What would Bezel do for my company?</button>
          <button class="prompt-pill" data-finn-prompt="How would you rebuild CRM AI first?">How would you rebuild CRM AI first?</button>
          <button class="prompt-pill" data-finn-prompt="I'm building agent workflows">I&rsquo;m building agent workflows</button>
          <button class="prompt-pill" data-finn-prompt="I want to book a strategy call">I want to book a strategy call</button>
        </div>

        <p class="finn-error" id="finnError" role="alert">
          Finn is temporarily unavailable. <a href="#booking">Book directly &rarr;</a>
        </p>

        <div class="finn-chat__input-area">
          <textarea class="finn-chat__input"
                    id="finnInput"
                    placeholder="Tell Finn what you&rsquo;re trying to build..."
                    aria-label="Message Finn"
                    rows="1"
                    maxlength="2000"></textarea>
          <button class="finn-chat__send"
                  id="finnSendBtn"
                  aria-label="Send message">
            Send
          </button>
        </div>
        <p class="finn-chat__subtitle">Chats may be reviewed by Dreamborn to understand demand and route serious inquiries.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <aside class="connect-rail" aria-label="Book a Dreamborn strategy call">
      <section class="connect-rail-panel connect-rail-panel--booking" id="booking">
        <div class="connect-booking-head">
          <p class="ops-panel-label">Executive handoff</p>
          <span>live route</span>
        </div>
        <h2>Start the handoff.</h2>
        <p>If the conversation is real, give Finn the context. Dreamborn can route serious inquiries from there.</p>

        <button class="btn btn--primary"
                type="button"
                data-finn-prompt="I want to route this to Dreamborn for a live strategy conversation.">
          Route through Finn
        </button>
      </section>
    </aside>
  </section>
</main>
